      <title>津巴布韦可能暂停限制非正规贸易、提高增值税的计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-07/zimbabwe-may-suspend-plan-to-restrict-informal-trade-raise-vat</link>
      <description><![CDATA[津巴布韦工业联合会在给成员的一份说明中表示，津巴布韦可能会暂停强制企业从合规和获得许可的实体采购商品的举措。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-07/zimbabwe-may-suspend-plan-to-restrict-informal-trade-raise-vat</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 07 Jan 2024 09:15:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>航空公司和监管机构对波音 737 Max 喷气式飞机采取行动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-07/the-airlines-and-regulators-taking-action-on-boeing-737-max-jets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[1 月 5 日阿拉斯加航空 1282 航班发生事故，波音公司 737 Max 飞机被迫停飞。迄今为止，其最受欢迎的飞机和最大的收入来源——再次成为众人瞩目的焦点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-07/the-airlines-and-regulators-taking-action-on-boeing-737-max-jets</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 07 Jan 2024 06:33:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国监管机构加大力度打击与中国相关的票据</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-07/south-korea-watchdog-intensifies-crackdown-on-china-linked-notes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国监管机构将对出售与中国股票相关的奇异票据的当地银行和经纪商展开更广泛的调查，担心这些证券可能会让投资者蒙受重大损失。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-07/south-korea-watchdog-intensifies-crackdown-on-china-linked-notes</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 07 Jan 2024 03:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国核心通胀放缓增强了美联储的乐观情绪</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-06/world-economy-latest-easing-us-core-inflation-seen-reinforcing-fed-optimism</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着 2023 年接近尾声，美国潜在的价格压力可能会继续消退，这支撑了美联储对通胀路径的乐观态度。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-06/world-economy-latest-easing-us-core-inflation-seen-reinforcing-fed-optimism</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 06 Jan 2024 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>航空公司遵循美国联邦航空局 (FAA) 指令，全球波音 Max 停飞</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-06/alaska-airlines-flight-makes-emergency-landing-in-portland-fox</link>
      <description><![CDATA[波音公司 737 Max 9 的停飞步伐迅速加快，在阿拉斯加航空公司一架全新飞机的机身部分在飞行过程中发生爆炸后，从美国到巴拿马再到土耳其的航空公司都将该机型停飞进行检查。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-06/alaska-airlines-flight-makes-emergency-landing-in-portland-fox</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 06 Jan 2024 03:54:23 GMT</pubDate>
